headline: Phillips 66 Faces $2.4M Fine for Alleged Oil Dumping in LA
summary: PSX has been indicted for allegedly dumping hundreds of thousands of gallons of oil-laden wastewater into Los Angeles' sewer system in 2020 and 2021.

headline: Wall Street Breakfast Podcast: DirecTV Drops Dish Deal Over Debt Dispute
summary: DirecTV scraps DISH acquisition on debt swap deadlock. Reddit drops on report holder seeks to sell $1.2B stake. Phillips 66 hit with federal charges for illegal wastewater dumping.
